These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, scientist
1. the electrician is in an even position##4
2. the scientist is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | cooking | writing |
| Job     | scientist    | electrician   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, australian
1. the chinese is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | folk |
| Nationality   | chinese | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, tomato
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | cola |
| Food       | pineapple | tomato    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
