 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, helicopter
1. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | cricket | biathlon  |
| Transport   | helicopter  | trike |

 #################################

 
